      <title>部长说，印度“接近降低商品及服务税，合理化利率。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-09/india-close-to-cutting-gst-rationalizing-rates-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长尼尔马拉·西塔拉曼（Nirmala Sitharaman）表示，印度几乎正在减少其商品和服务税，并在合理化利率方面的工作处于最后阶段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-09/india-close-to-cutting-gst-rationalizing-rates-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Mar 2025 06:10:56 GMT</pubDate>
