    <item>
      <title>中国的通货膨胀率在一年中首次下降到零以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-09/china-consumer-inflation-drops-below-zero-for-first-time-in-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的消费者通货膨胀率远远超过了13个月以来首次降至零以下的预期，这一评估因季节性扭曲而偏向，但在经济中持续存在压力的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-09/china-consumer-inflation-drops-below-zero-for-first-time-in-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Mar 2025 01:44:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
